(62, 1, '2021-08-31 14:13:48', '2021-08-31 13:13:48', 'The <strong>Epiphone EB-0</strong> is an affordable SG Bass, with vintage tone offered up by a single Sidewinder humbucking pickup. A supremely affordable 4-string for any level of player.\r\n<h3>A classic 60\'s bass that anyone can afford!</h3>\r\nThanks to their partnership with Gibson, Epiphone have been able to re-issue some of the most classic guitars ever made. The EB-0 bass is no different - drawing from the iconic 60s solidbody design of the SG, incorporated into a 4-string bass. A shorter 30.5\" scale length means that even smaller or first-time players can appreciate its feel and comfort, without compromise to tone, set-up or style.\r\n\r\nThe benchmark performance and rich tone of the EB0 is down to the shorter scale length. Not only does it make it much more playable for smaller or younger players, it gives this bass a unique rock \'growl\' thanks to the shorter strings.\r\n\r\nBill Wyman of The Rolling Stones, Jack Bruce from Cream, and John Entwistle from The Who have all found a place in their hearts for the EB-0 SG Bass. If it\'s good enough for these rock icons, it\'s good enough for us!\r\n\r\n<b>Epiphone EB-0 Features:</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Body Shape:</strong> SG</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Left-/Right-handed:</strong> Right-handed</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Number of Strings:</strong> 4</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Colour:</strong> Cherry</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Body Material:</strong> Mahogany</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Body Finish:</strong> Urethane</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Neck Material:</strong> Mahogany, Bolt-on</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Neck Shape:</strong> SlimTaper D Profile</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Fingerboard Inlay:</strong> White Dots</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Scale Length:</strong> 30.5\"</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Number of Frets:</strong> 20</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Nut Width:</strong> 1.50\"</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Bridge/Tailpiece:</strong> Adjustable Bridge</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Tuners:</strong> Nickel Tuners</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Number of Pickups:</strong> 1</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Neck Pickup:</strong> Sidewinder Humbucking Pickup</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Controls:</strong> Volume, Tone</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Manufacturer Part Number:</strong> EBG0CHCH1</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Epiphone EB-0 SG Electric Bass', 'The <strong>Epiphone EB-0</strong> is an affordable SG Bass, with vintage tone offered up by a single Sidewinder humbucking pickup. A supremely affordable 4-string for any level of player.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'epiphone-eb-0-sg-electric-bass', '', '', '2021-09-01 13:59:10', '2021-09-01 12:59:10', '', 0, 'http://localhost/?post_type=product&#038;p=62', 0, 'product', '', 0),
