(65, 1, '2021-08-31 14:28:41', '2021-08-31 13:28:41', 'The <strong>Epiphone EB-3 Electric Bass Guitar Gloss Ebony</strong> is inspired by the legendary EB \"SG\" - Gibson\'s first electric bass guitar.\r\n\r\nWith its familiar dual-cutaway body design, super-playable neck, and thunderous pickups, this is the ultimate entry-level bass for the aspiring rocker.\r\n<h4>Epiphone EB-3 Electric Bass Guitar Gloss Ebony Highlights</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Sleek, versatile bass with the iconic SG body shape</li>\r\n 	<li>Inspired by the original EB \"SG\" bass, as used by the likes of Jack Bruce and John Entwistle</li>\r\n 	<li>Classic dual cutaway Mahogany body, and super-sleek fast neck</li>\r\n 	<li>Sidewinder Humbucker and NYT mini humbucker pickup configuration</li>\r\n 	<li>Independent Volume and Tone controls for each pickup, along with a 3-way rotary selector switch</li>\r\n 	<li>Stylish Trapezoid fret markers</li>\r\n 	<li>Epiphone Limited Lifetime warranty (see Epiphone website for more details)</li>\r\n 	<li>Perfect for complete beginners and more experienced players alike</li>\r\n 	<li>Superb value for money</li>\r\n 	<li>Home Delivery options available</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Hard-Rocking, Super-Playable Bass at a Great Price!</h3>\r\nIn addition to the lightweight double-cutaway body design, the Epiphone EB-3 is equipped with a long-scale neck. This neck ensures the bass delivers a superb amount of natural sustain, as well as articulate tone.\r\n\r\nThis sleek, 34\" scale, slim-taper neck fits easily into your hand, making the EB-3 ideal for relative beginners as well as guitarists looking to make the switch into low-end territory.\r\n<h4>Vintage EB-Tone</h4>\r\nPart of the EB-3\'s charm has always been the smooth, no-nonesense tones it produces. This is down to the combination of a Sidewinder humbucker at the neck, and that famous NYT mini-humbucker at the bridge.\r\n\r\nThese pickups perfectly compliment the natural tonal properties of the Mahogany body, which resul